### ValueSet: CAVE Typ - $expand
# @name expand
GET {{baseUrl}}/ValueSet/cave-typ/$expand
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

### ValueSet: CAVE Typ - $validate-code valid (allergie)
# @name validate_valid_1
GET {{baseUrl}}/ValueSet/cave-typ/$validate-code?system=https://fhir.cognovis.de/praxis/CodeSystem/cave-typ&code=allergie
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

### ValueSet: CAVE Typ - $validate-code valid (unvertraeglichkeit)
